WEBVTT

00:00.434 --> 00:02.029
<i>Previously on</i> Sanctuary...

00:02.029 --> 00:03.764
You want something kept
hidden or off the grid,

00:03.766 --> 00:05.537
Richard Feliz is your man.

00:05.538 --> 00:06.803
Thanks to my resources,

00:06.805 --> 00:08.572
your financial future
will be very healthy

00:08.574 --> 00:09.673
for quite some time.

00:09.675 --> 00:10.840
Thank you, Richard.

00:10.842 --> 00:12.708
This is a personal
energy shield

00:12.710 --> 00:14.412
that acts like body armor.

00:14.414 --> 00:16.146
Now, it's a work in progress,

00:16.149 --> 00:18.649
but once I iron out
the last few kinks,

00:18.651 --> 00:20.151
this baby's going
to change the world.

00:21.187 --> 00:22.520
I'm not too proud to admit

00:22.522 --> 00:24.757
that I am <i> very</i> used
to getting my own way.

00:24.759 --> 00:25.792
You shut me down.

00:25.794 --> 00:28.362
You've been a wonderful
soldier, Will.

00:28.364 --> 00:31.701
You have done everything
I've asked you and more.

00:31.703 --> 00:34.471
The fear of abnormals
is so pervasive in Washington

00:34.473 --> 00:35.806
that when they came back
a second time,

00:35.808 --> 00:37.709
they basically
offered me a blank check.

00:37.711 --> 00:39.845
He used the government money
to fund his own research.

00:39.847 --> 00:41.747
Skimmed off the top.

00:41.749 --> 00:43.248
Doctor, I have
a room full of recordings

00:43.250 --> 00:45.651
of your boy here

00:45.653 --> 00:48.620
coordinating, planning,
fraternizing with creatures

00:48.622 --> 00:50.522
I consider to be public enemies
number one through five.

00:50.524 --> 00:53.425
<i>From below,</i>

00:53.427 --> 00:55.793
<i>we rise.</i>

00:55.795 --> 00:57.429
You need to know
how serious this is.

00:57.431 --> 00:58.529
Now, I am
advising you

00:58.531 --> 01:00.731
to stay well out of my way.

01:00.733 --> 01:01.799
If you don't,

01:01.801 --> 01:03.735
I will come after you, too.

01:03.737 --> 01:05.370
You're not yourself.

01:05.373 --> 01:06.706
You've been brainwashed.

01:06.708 --> 01:10.610
I pledge to serve
the cause that is just.

01:10.612 --> 01:11.544
You don't have to do this.

01:15.684 --> 01:17.617
He's getting better.

01:17.619 --> 01:19.219
Magnus has been trying
to undo the damage

01:19.221 --> 01:20.888
done by the Crixorum.

01:20.890 --> 01:22.290
He feels terrible
about what happened.

01:24.694 --> 01:28.497
From below, we rise.

01:30.000 --> 01:36.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:40.478 --> 01:41.678
I'm not coming in.

01:41.680 --> 01:44.715
The residents are all secure,
I assure you.

01:44.717 --> 01:46.150
There's only one monster
that I'm worried about.

01:46.152 --> 01:47.485
Please...

01:47.487 --> 01:50.621
I haven't bitten a guest
in decades.

01:50.623 --> 01:52.623
You've been flying all night.

01:52.625 --> 01:54.825
Let me make you a meal,
a nice glass of wine--

01:54.827 --> 01:56.894
See? Right there.
Feminine charms,

01:56.896 --> 01:57.861
wiles,

01:57.863 --> 01:59.563
beguiling behavior.

01:59.565 --> 02:00.665
I will not have it.

02:00.667 --> 02:01.566
I will not have it.

02:01.568 --> 02:03.501
Get in.

02:03.503 --> 02:05.036
Right.

02:06.506 --> 02:08.139
Now, as to why I'm here--

02:08.142 --> 02:09.842
Not the wine?

02:09.844 --> 02:12.178
Please, just let me
get through this.

02:13.582 --> 02:17.951
You want to quit as my banker.

02:17.953 --> 02:21.523
I want to be released
from my duties, yes.

02:21.525 --> 02:23.158
No.

02:23.160 --> 02:24.660
Helen, when I come here
in person,

02:24.662 --> 02:27.062
it's because I'm serious.

02:27.064 --> 02:29.031
Plus, you kept hanging up on me.

02:29.033 --> 02:30.166
Well, you're here now.

02:30.168 --> 02:31.601
At least take a moment
to freshen up.

02:31.603 --> 02:33.303
I cannot keep doing this.

02:33.305 --> 02:35.305
I thoroughly respect
the work you're doing.

02:35.307 --> 02:37.241
The things you are
hoping to accomplish

02:37.243 --> 02:38.642
are of epic proportions,

02:38.644 --> 02:41.145
and I have been honored
to have been part of it--

02:41.147 --> 02:42.212
But?

02:42.214 --> 02:43.280
But I quit.

02:43.282 --> 02:44.282
I said no.

02:44.284 --> 02:45.149
Then fire me.

02:45.151 --> 02:45.950
On what grounds,
cowardice?

02:45.952 --> 02:46.784
If that works, yes.

02:46.786 --> 02:48.620
Am I out of money?

02:48.622 --> 02:49.855
No.

02:49.857 --> 02:51.189
But it's what you want me
to do with it.

02:51.191 --> 02:54.260
I've run out
of moves, Helen.

02:54.262 --> 02:57.096
I've done everything
I can to hide your money,

02:57.098 --> 02:58.564
grow it,

02:58.566 --> 03:01.767
put it in places
that only you can access,

03:01.769 --> 03:04.737
but the cost has been too much,

03:04.739 --> 03:07.073
especially

03:07.075 --> 03:08.974
with what
you're planning.

03:08.976 --> 03:10.776
Now...

03:10.778 --> 03:12.711
I adore you,

03:12.713 --> 03:15.314
but this has got to be
the end of the line for me.

03:15.316 --> 03:16.582
I hope you understand.

03:20.187 --> 03:22.054
And you did come in person.

03:22.056 --> 03:24.691
How could I not?

03:24.693 --> 03:26.693
It's you.

03:32.133 --> 03:33.734
You've been
a wonderful friend,

03:33.736 --> 03:36.003
and a vital ally in this war.

03:36.005 --> 03:37.238
I can't thank you enough
for all that you've done.

03:37.240 --> 03:40.075
Oh, it's been my pleasure.

03:40.077 --> 03:41.675
And if there's
anything you need,

03:41.677 --> 03:43.411
one of my villas,
a boat,

03:43.413 --> 03:44.812
a well-dressed
dinner companion...

03:47.014 --> 03:49.382
There is
one last favor, actually.

03:50.684 --> 03:51.918
No.

03:51.920 --> 03:54.053
Come on,
you're leaving me high and dry.

03:54.055 --> 03:55.087
It's the very least you can do.

03:55.089 --> 03:56.289
What, now?

03:56.291 --> 03:58.190
Well, it seems perfect.

03:58.192 --> 04:01.160
I think... 12 minutes
should be enough for me.

04:01.162 --> 04:03.162
Oh, I knew I should
never have stepped

04:03.164 --> 04:06.633
into this bloody house.

04:13.309 --> 04:16.343
Andre? Yes, it's Richard.

04:16.345 --> 04:18.646
I'd like you...

04:18.648 --> 04:20.113
to execute

04:20.116 --> 04:22.717
maneuver Delta Epsilon.

04:22.719 --> 04:24.251
Yes, right now.

04:24.253 --> 04:25.419
No.

04:25.421 --> 04:27.154
This is not a drill.

04:27.156 --> 04:28.889
Just do it.

04:31.058 --> 04:33.759
Well, I hope you're happy.

04:33.761 --> 04:36.729
I've just shut down Wall Street
for 12 minutes.

04:39.867 --> 04:41.066
About that wine.

04:41.068 --> 04:42.200
Ah.

04:44.004 --> 04:47.406
Do you have anything
that is a little naughty?

04:53.815 --> 04:55.082
Go, go!

04:55.084 --> 04:56.116
Stop him!

05:00.422 --> 05:02.790
Please...

05:02.792 --> 05:03.757
I have nothing.

05:03.759 --> 05:06.126
Leave him alone!

05:06.128 --> 05:07.761
You walk away,

05:07.763 --> 05:09.062
nobody gets hurt.

05:17.738 --> 05:19.105
Can you fight?

05:19.107 --> 05:20.172
I can hardly see.

05:20.174 --> 05:22.274
Just follow my lead.

05:22.276 --> 05:23.109
Come on...

05:26.381 --> 05:27.480
Leave now

05:27.482 --> 05:29.048
if you want to stay alive.

05:30.084 --> 05:31.184
Go.

05:33.321 --> 05:34.187
Go!

05:44.965 --> 05:46.065
My life is yours.

05:46.067 --> 05:48.801
Not up here, brother.

05:48.803 --> 05:51.271
Nice shooting.

05:51.273 --> 05:53.206
It's primitive,

05:53.208 --> 05:55.275
awkwardly balanced.

05:55.277 --> 05:57.511
We have better weapons
where I come from.

05:59.247 --> 06:00.947
I'm sure you do.

06:05.420 --> 06:08.388
If I wanted
to shoot you,

06:08.390 --> 06:11.357
I would have done so
already, Will.

06:15.895 --> 06:17.162
Do I know you?

06:17.164 --> 06:18.963
Not yet.

06:18.965 --> 06:20.264
I'm Caleb.

06:22.268 --> 06:23.401
As in Hollow Earth Caleb?

06:24.870 --> 06:25.870
The most wanted man

06:25.872 --> 06:27.272
according to human authorities.

06:27.274 --> 06:28.774
And, yes, I know who you are,

06:28.776 --> 06:30.843
and what you do.

06:30.845 --> 06:32.978
I think it would be
a good idea

06:32.980 --> 06:35.114
if Jebal came with you
to the Sanctuary.

06:35.116 --> 06:38.851
He'll be safe there
while things calm down out here.

06:40.387 --> 06:42.889
Yeah, I think you're right.

06:42.891 --> 06:45.358
You tell Helen Magnus

06:45.360 --> 06:48.261
she's got a new friend in town.

06:55.439 --> 06:59.439
<font color=#00FF00>♪ Sanctuary 4x12 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Sanctuary for None, Part I</font>
